---
// It might not be a sprint, but it can be a 5k.
---
<div class="flex flex-col gap-y-4">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold">
        Overcome the techno-babble
    </h2>
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-x-8">
        <div class="flex flex-col gap-y-4">
            <h3 class="text-xl">Humans Are Silly</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-500">
                I've spent the better part of five years learning how search systems
                are built and deployed at some of the largest companies.

            </p>
            <p class="text-gray-500">
                I can help you deploy Full Text Search, Semantic Search, or
                how to simply improve the UX of your store to help increase conversions.
            </p>

        </div>
        <div class="flex flex-col gap-y-4">
            <h3 class="text-xl">Order to Cash</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-500">
                I understand more than programming languages. I understand the
                language of business. I can help developers navigate the specific
                languages or ERPs and WMSs.
            </p>
        </div>
        <div class="flex flex-col gap-y-4">
            <h3 class="text-xl">Embrace a Product Mindset</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-500">
                The number of systems that are involved in the customer's journey
                requires a broad overview of the entire flow and knowing how
                to stay "on brand" at each touch point.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>